::Ramulus/Smokescreen/Zeus/Killer::

One of Ramulus' eyebrows rise at Hot Rod's show of command, but the ram makes 
no comment. He turns around, firing his big gun at Anubis.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Smokscreen sighs as he sees the newcomers run up. Didn't those idiots ever 
give up?! He runs toward Serpentor, firing at him.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Zeus flies into the battlefield in his beast mode, firing two missiles at 
Savanah.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
"YEEHAA!!" Killer yells as he runs into the scene, firing his rapid fire 
rifle at Hot Rod.
